message.content: a kitchen with dark gray cabinets, and beige marble counter tops; a white refrigerator between the kitchen cabinets; a pot on an induction cooker on the counter top to the right of the sink; the sink placed on the left side of the counter; a range hood above the induction cooker; a cupboard above the counter with the sink; boxes of "Chicky", "Rice Bubbles", and "Jello", jars, a stack of plates, and a gallon of water on the counter; a dining table with a box of "Shortbread", a jug, a wine glass, a plate and a gallon of water on top; white chairs around the table; a round light on the white ceiling.
